{"tid":2453334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁大件事冇人講？？［save12］8人將於下週一刑滿返香港","createTime":"2021-03-19T11:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T13:56:31.000Z","uid":391580,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7f6dae0022077f3facaac97cefc2c2be1c37aa5e","tid":2453334,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"12名港人在中國被捕判刑一案，其中8人刑滿出獄，將於下周一早上經深圳灣口岸返港，移交給香港警方、然後會解往天水圍警署扣留。<br />\n<br />\n深圳市鹽田區人民法院於去年底將其中10 人裁定因組織他人偷越邊境罪罪成的鄧棨然判囚3年、喬映瑜判囚2年，分別處罰2萬及1.5萬元人民幣；至於因偷越邊境罪罪成的李宇軒、鄭子豪等8人，則分別判囚7個月及處罰1萬元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n當中有兩名未成年少年獲免起訴，並且在去年底由內地移交返港的港人廖子文及黃臨福，經深圳灣口岸返港。"},{"pid":"3df03444c9c982148290cf650b5fb5f4ac908684","tid":2453334,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T13:15:13.000Z","msg":"無人講咪你講"},{"pid":"51bc161cd6b8d09fad86b71e0c75247e80376e03","tid":2453334,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T13:17:26.000Z","msg":"有人已經講咗啦!"},{"pid":"a8d2add186afcec5c0c51be70e78924f65c0bb97","tid":2453334,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T13:17:31.000Z","msg":"坐咁少？"},{"pid":"ee8d682b6eb1b06dcdff6bfb60a25e20c6d6c65e","tid":2453334,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T13:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51da031f5f61bd664cf878a0ce106a2586437786","tid":2453334,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"返到黎仲要俾港共政府清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}